data.description: Come see this beautiful well kept home in this charming neighborhood on a Cul- de- sac. Great yard for both kids and pets. Large storage shed, new paint and laminate flooring through out the whole house . Living room with large windows that brings lots of sunshine in! Large sun room off the family room great for entertaining that leads to your back yard oasis with mature trees and landscaping for privacy. 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 1,999 sq. ft. Close to Hwy 99 for an easy commute with shopping, parks and health clubs near by
